course_title: Advanced Studies in Music Theory - ART SONG ANALYS

sections.comments: Analytical approaches to song, beginning with 19th-century Lieder then exploring a variety of art songs from diverse cultures and composers. Open to DMA and MMus Composition students with permission of the instructor.

description: Research seminar on a core or emerging topic in music theory. May be repeated to a maximum of 12 credits if different topics are covered.
